<p>LordBeauremont:<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup> Hey! Welcome to Massy's Big Chance. You say you're new here?</p>
