<p>26Thulu62: Sweet! And hey, it's got graphics, too! How many different forms are there? Whoa, check out the customization!</p>
<p>LordBeauremont: It's really sweet. Here, check it out, I decided I had to troll all the humans we encounter. Since they can't have kids, I thought, what better than to look like a big baby? I went all out. Green eyes, black nose, you know, just like a human baby. I even got to trade out the flower power to expel feces, instead.</p>
