<p>LordBeauremont: Nope. The devs (the idiots keep spelling it &quot;divs&quot;) said that if we're going to be gods, our actions should have lasting effects, and besides, this world's dying and when it gets out of beta they'll put everyone in a whole new world that's not dying out.</p>
